  "content": "# Custom Schemas\n\nThese schema registry files define local extensions to XanaNode Core.\n\nCustom types should be:\n\n- namespaced\n- described in human-readable language\n- versioned\n- mappable to a core type when possible\n- safe to preserve even when another implementation does not fully understand them\n",
